\end{bmatrix}
\end{equation*}\]

<p>ä¸ºäº†æœ€å°åŒ–æŸå¤±å‡½æ•°ï¼Œ$\mathop{min}\limits{\theta}J(\theta)$</p>

\[\begin{equation*} 
\theta=(x^{T}X+\lambda
\begin{bmatrix}
0&amp;0&amp;0&amp;\ldots&amp;0  \\
